### Getting Started
Here are a few resources to help you get started:
- [Team Handbook](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1ZXubgBkNFCrBxMWcdJX_Ah2cNDKHd9cAsCCRqaXAee8/edit#heading=h.80uwye99rlpl)
